@zoewintersx @zrubenf1 @Marlonif @Alts_Anonymous @remnynt @borg_brain This isn't possible yet. The MNLTH doesn't actually contain a 3D model in its Metadata.

RTFKT worked with OnCyber to make this happen. It's a custom setup created for RTFKTs MNLTH.

We may see this ability in the future though.

@MiccoloSolis If you receive an error buying something on polygon through Opensea. Wait 30 minutes. It'll most likely still go through.

Your transaction was created its just waiting for network congestion to dip into an area that your transaction gets picked up.

It'll show up as an offer.
